## Install
* User: <span style="color:red;font-weight:bold;">root</span>
  * Use "sudo" if you wish.
  * Change Directory (cd) to the linux kernel source!

```
# USER: ROOT ============
make modules_install

make install

make headers_install INSTALL_HDR_PATH=/usr

```

